## Common Observability Metrics

| Metric | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Latency | Time taken by each node |
| Tokens Used | Input and output token count |
| Execution Time | Total workflow duration |
| Success Rate | Percentage of successful executions |
| Error Count | Number of failures |
| Retry Count | Number of retries performed |

